# m1_big_fall.shot — large drop, look for leg-into-ground.
#
# Jet up until fuel is spent (~1.67 s of full thrust), release, free-fall
# back to the floor. Bursts shots through the impact tick by tick so we
# can see if the foot/knee particles end up below the tile surface or
# oscillate after settling.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/fall
aim    520 200

at 10 shot stand_t010

# Climb. fuel_max is 1.0, drains 0.6/sec → ~100 ticks of jet available.
at 30 press jet
burst climb from 50 to 130 every 20
at 130 release jet

# Free fall — capture the descent.
burst air from 140 to 240 every 15

# Impact window — sample every 5 ticks to see clipping/oscillation.
burst impact from 245 to 320 every 5

# Settled (or still bouncing).
burst settle from 330 to 500 every 25

at 540 end
